# Windows-only toolchain pin — must NOT reach the Linux container build (it pins a
# stable-x86_64-pc-windows-gnu channel that fails on Linux). Cargo uses the image default.
rust-toolchain.toml
# Windows-only cargo config (target-dir = "C:/mx_target") — the C: path is invalid on
# Linux and breaks the build. Let cargo use its default ./target in the container.
.cargo
